data.description: REDUCED!  Best Price per Square Foot in Ocean Pines!  Greetings and welcome to 10 Starboard Court!  Great Square Footage!  This detached rancher is located on a quiet cul-de-sac in North Ocean Pines, featuring a partly wooded, level, high and dry lot. The generously sized gravel driveway provides ample parking for the homeowner and guests. The main-level living floor plan is perfect for your first home or vacation getaway. Upon entering, you'll find a spacious living room with a bay window and electric fireplace for that extra warm feeling. The large kitchen features newer stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, a center island with additional counter space, and is open to the dining room area. Sliding glass doors lead to an abundantly sized sunroom /3-season room, providing extra main-level living space. The primary bedroom has a double-door closet and a full bath with a stall shower. Both additional bedrooms are well-sized with full-sized hall bath with a linen closet and tub/shower. The home offers plenty of storage with pull-down stairs accessible to the attic space. A whole-house fan is present as well. The level rear yard has a large shed for all your tools and outdoor equipment needs. Most windows have been updated and replaced in this home. This is a perfect opportunity to own a nicely maintained home in the desirable community of Ocean Pines. This is it if you want a home to include your personal touches and design ideas!  Solidly constructed throughout, come to 10 Starboard Court and create your picture-perfect home or vacation getaway.
